{"tid":2380524,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【Fake News盡在香港】利君已被終止公務員合約，但港媒繼續宣傳只是延長120天試用期！！！！！！","createTime":"2021-01-26T03:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T03:12:39.000Z","uid":88743,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fda218cfa50273f65bee463e68b50cc12614c324","tid":2380524,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:03:46.000Z","msg":"之前睇呢個PO以為真係延長試用期<br />\n<br />\n蘋果：利君雅再被延長120天試用期<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2375489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2375489</a><br />\n<br />\n我前幾日一直以為只係延長試用期，今日先聽人講原來俾人炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多數都係標題Fake News, 咁都已經夠死<br />\n蘋果應該已經改返，但仲有好多傳媒今時今日都仲未改<br />\n應該係專登用呢隻字昆鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">Fake News:<br />\n<br />\n明報</span></strong><br />\n利君雅被要求簽新合約<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">延120天試用期</span></span></strong> 如不簽等同離職 工會批「花式炒人」 (15:36)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3rtdru.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3rtdru.png&h=5624e0cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <code>https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20210122/s00001/1611299082643/利君雅被要求簽新合約延120天試用期-如不簽等同離職-工會批「花式炒人」</code><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">01</span></strong><br />\n利君雅調查報告遲出爐 <strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">試用期再延長120日</span></span></strong> 要求7日內簽新約｜香港01｜政情<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z9u22jT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ9u22jT.png&h=e53bea3d&s={SIZE}\" /> <code>https://www.hk01.com/政情/578012/利君雅調查報告遲出爐-試用期再延長120日-要求7日內簽新約</code><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><strong>True News:<br />\n<br />\nRTHK</strong></span><br />\n港台工會表示，助理節目主任利君雅<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"violet\">原有公務員試用期合約將被終止</span></strong></span>，管方以未完成調查為由，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"violet\">向她<ins>另開一份為期120日的聘用合約，公務員約滿酬金被扣起</ins></span></strong></span>，工會感到憤怒和失望。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t93GyeR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft93GyeR.png&h=cc6311c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/4215090468598977/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F4215090468598977%2F&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=23de6d34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/4215090468598977/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"violet\">自由亞洲電台RFA</span></strong><br />\n利君雅<span class=\"violet\"><strong>試用期「被完結」</strong></span>　工會：管方擺出 「此處不留人」官威<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-reporter-01222021043756.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-reporter-01222021043756.html&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=694e7651\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-reporter-01222021043756.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"violet\">中央社CNA</span></strong><br />\n香港電台<span class=\"violet\"><strong>將終止記者公務員合約</strong></span> 工會：憤怒失望<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202101220205.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202101220205.aspx&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=4c6aa34d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202101220205.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果今次我就撐你啦<br />\n<strong><span class=\"violet\">蘋果日報</span></strong><br />\n利君雅<strong><span class=\"violet\">試用期「被完結」 港台管理層「花式炒人」</span></strong>稱調查未完<strong><span class=\"violet\">另開120日臨時約</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210122/IK676FZKQNFMZKDV6XRZVTELSI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210122